This paper deals with the analysis of VPN usage and censorship circumvention, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The use of DNS cache snooping to determine which domains are being accessed through VPNs involves network infrastructure (cs.NI) and cyber security (cs.CY). The paper also discusses the limitations of the technique used, which could be considered as a study in systems and information theory (cs.SI). Finally, the paper involves data analysis and statistics, which could be classified under data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
